room_title: Escape room "SOS: Sasquatch on Site" by paradigmQ in Portland
room_address: 14415 SE Mill Plain Blvd #104B Vancouver, WA 98684
room_description: An eccentric Sasquatch hunter, on the verge of a crytpo-zoological breakthrough, has gone missing. Her last known location is an abandoned cabin near Mount St. Helens. Can you save her life, or at least, uncover the truth? Either way, something big is afoot.
